==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Fore-topmast
<hw>Fore`-top"mast</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Naut.)</fld>
<def>The mast erected at the head of the foremast, and at the head of
which stands the fore-topgallant mast; the mast next above the foremast.
See <er>Ship</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Fore-topsail</ent>⟦br⟧
